    wcGeneSummary

    textORA

    textORA.Rd

    Return p-values from hypergeometric distribution (experimental)

    Usage

    textORA(queries)

    Arguments

    queries

    gene list (Entrez ID)

    Value

    p-values for the words

    p-values for the words

    Examples
